{
  "video_id": "cYC55Fw80zM",
  "title": "Legal Analysis: When does making threats become a crime?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6120.0,
      "end_time": 9750.0,
      "text": "As a criminal defense lawyer, people ask me all the time--"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9750.0,
      "end_time": 13360.0,
      "text": "when I was making a threat against somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 13360.0,
      "end_time": 14620.0,
      "text": "become a crime?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14620.0,
      "end_time": 18390.0,
      "text": "And the answer is that under Penal Code Section 422, which"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18390.0,
      "end_time": 20980.0,
      "text": "defines a crime of criminal threats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 20980.0,
      "end_time": 24360.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a crime when you threatened to kill or injure"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24360.0,
      "end_time": 26790.0,
      "text": "somebody or somebody close to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 26790.0,
      "end_time": 29530.0,
      "text": "when your intention is to put them in fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29530.0,
      "end_time": 32950.0,
      "text": "and you actually do put them in, what the law calls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32950.0,
      "end_time": 34380.0,
      "text": "sustained fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34380.0,
      "end_time": 36780.0,
      "text": "So sustained fear means that the person"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36780.0,
      "end_time": 39370.0,
      "text": "was in fear not just for a brief moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39370.0,
      "end_time": 42239.0,
      "text": "but for some period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42240.0,
      "end_time": 45760.0,
      "text": "Now, examples of this are calling your ex-girlfriend"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45760.0,
      "end_time": 49500.0,
      "text": "and threatening to shoot her and her new boyfriend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49500.0,
      "end_time": 52529.0,
      "text": "or a disgruntled customer who calls a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52530.0,
      "end_time": 55600.0,
      "text": "and threatens to blow up their building."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55600.0,
      "end_time": 57170.0,
      "text": "If your intention is to put them in fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57170.0,
      "end_time": 59860.0,
      "text": "and you actually do put them in sustained fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59860.0,
      "end_time": 62970.0,
      "text": "you can be charged with criminal threats."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62970.0,
      "end_time": 66500.0,
      "text": "Now, criminal threats is a very serious crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66500.0,
      "end_time": 68500.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a wobbler, which means it can be filed"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68500.0,
      "end_time": 70950.0,
      "text": "as a misdemeanor or a felony."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70950.0,
      "end_time": 74920.0,
      "text": "As a felony, it can carry up to three years in custody."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74920.0,
      "end_time": 77680.0,
      "text": "But moreover, as a felony, it counts"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77680.0,
      "end_time": 80860.0,
      "text": "as a strike under California&#39;s Three Strikes law."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80860.0,
      "end_time": 84200.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re convicted, it&#39;s something that could ultimately"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84200.0,
      "end_time": 87200.0,
      "text": "contribute towards putting you in prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87200.0,
      "end_time": 89210.0,
      "text": "for the rest of your life."
    }
  ]
}